text: The Nissan Titan is a mid-size pickup truck that is built by Nissan. The Nissan Titan is in its second generation. The Titan started being created on September 21, 2003. It was designed by Diane Allen. ==References== ==Other websites== *Nissan Titan on Nissan.com *Nissan Titan on Nissan.ca Titan Category:Pickup trucks Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles Category:2020s automobiles
